text: Koku Ahiaku (born 6 March 1963) is a Togolese former cyclist. He competed in the individual road race at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1963 births Category:Living people Category:Togolese male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Togo Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
